courses.title: Guided Studies
courses.description: To attend seminars/workshops and carry out assignments for the purposes of increasing knowledge of the research area and improving experimental design and data analysis.
courses.enrollment_requirement: For students in MPhil Medical Sciences
courses.learning_outcomes: Acquire advanced knowledge in major areas of an academic discipline while maintaining a broad understanding of other related fields.

courses.feedback_evaluation: Please refer to the supervisor's guidance.
courses.required_readings: Please refer to the supervisor's guidance.

courses.description: To conduct research work on the assigned research topic.
courses.enrollment_requirement: For students in MPhil Medical Sciences
courses.learning_outcomes:
Acquire advanced knowledge in major areas of an academic discipline.
Develop the ability to formulate individual research tasks and to develop solution methodologies under minimal supervision.
Gain proficiency in techniques of knowledge dissemination through manuscript writing.
